                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm glass-card p-4">
                        <div class="fs-1 mb-3">💳</div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark" style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Faturamento TISS XML</h5>
                        <p class="text-xs text-muted mb-0">Lotes de guias gerados automaticamente a partir das sessões para envio rápido aos convênios.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm glass-card p-4">
                        <div class="fs-1 mb-3">🌸</div>
                        <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark" style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Home Guidance</h5>
                        <p class="text-xs text-muted mb-0">Orientação prática contextual para que os pais reforcem os treinos terapêuticos em casa.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- SaaS Pricing Plans (Tabela de Planos) -->
            <div class="row mb-5 justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-12 text-center mb-5">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold text-dark"><i class="fa fa-credit-card me-2 text-primary"></i>Planos de Assinatura Simplificados</h3>
                    <p class="text-muted text-sm">Escolha o plano ideal para o tamanho da sua clínica. Todos incluem 14 dias de teste grátis.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Plano Bronze -->
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm glass-card p-4 d-flex flex-column">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-1">Plano Bronze</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-muted">Ideal para Terapeutas Autônomos</p>
                        <div class="my-4">
                            <span class="display-6 fw-bold text-dark">R$ 199</span>
                            <span class="text-muted">/mês</span>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled text-sm text-start mb-5 flex-grow-1">
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> 1 Profissional / Terapeuta</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> Até 5 Pacientes cadastrados</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> Objetivos Terapêuticos e Evoluções</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> Prontuário Clínico & Timeline</li>
                            <li class="mb-2 text-muted text-decoration-line-through"><i class="fa fa-times me-2"></i> Faturamento TISS XML</li>
                        </ul>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill w-100 OpenRegisterTrialModalButton" data-plan="Bronze">
                            Experimentar Bronze Grátis
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Plano Prata (Recomendado) -->
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-primary border-2 shadow p-4 d-flex flex-column position-relative" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); border-radius: 20px; border: 2px solid var(--color-mint-teal-base) !important;">
                        <span class="badge rounded-pill position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-3 px-3 py-2 text-white fw-bold" style="background: var(--gradient-welcoming-interactive); font-size: 0.7rem;">MAIS ESCOLHIDO</span>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-1">Plano Prata</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-muted">Para Clínicas em Crescimento</p>
                        <div class="my-4">
                            <span class="display-6 fw-bold text-primary" style="color: var(--color-mint-teal-base) !important;">R$ 499</span>
                            <span class="text-muted">/mês</span>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled text-sm text-start mb-5 flex-grow-1">
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> <strong>Até 5 Terapeutas</strong> ativos</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> <strong>Pacientes Ilimitados</strong></li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> Objetivos Terapêuticos e Evoluções</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> <strong>Faturamento TISS XML</strong> incluso</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> Portal da Família (Home Guidance)</li>
                        </ul>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-interactive rounded-pill w-100 OpenRegisterTrialModalButton" data-plan="Prata">
                            Experimentar Prata Grátis
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Plano Ouro -->
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm glass-card p-4 d-flex flex-column">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-1">Plano Ouro</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-muted">Para Clínicas e Redes Consolidadas</p>
                        <div class="my-4">
                            <span class="display-6 fw-bold text-dark">Custom</span>
                            <span class="text-muted">/mês</span>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled text-sm text-start mb-5 flex-grow-1">
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> Terapeutas & Pacientes Ilimitados</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> Faturamento TISS XML Ilimitado</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> <strong>White-Label Completo</strong></li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> Multi-tenant Isolado</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i> Gerente de Contas Dedicado</li>
                        </ul>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill w-100 OpenRegisterTrialModalButton" data-plan="Ouro">
                            Falar com Vendas
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Register Trial Modal -->
            <div class="modal fade" id="RegisterTrialModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="RegisterTrialModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
                    <div class="modal-content border-0 shadow-lg rounded-4 overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="modal-header bg-gradient-primary text-white border-0 p-4" style="background: var(--gradient-welcoming-interactive); color: white;">
                            <h5 class="modal-title fw-bold" id="RegisterTrialModalLabel">
                                <i class="fa fa-rocket me-2"></i>Iniciar Teste Grátis de 14 Dias
                            </h5>
                            <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal-body p-4 bg-light">
                            <form id="registerTrialForm" method="post" asp-page-handler="RegisterTrial">
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label class="form-label fw-semibold text-dark">Plano Escolhido</label>
                                    <select class="form-select" asp-for="TrialInput.SelectedPlan" id="TrialInput_SelectedPlan" required>
                                        <option value="Bronze">Plano Bronze - R$ 199/mês</option>
                                        <option value="Prata">Plano Prata (Recomendado) - R$ 499/mês</option>
                                        <option value="Ouro">Plano Ouro (Enterprise) - Sob Consulta</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label class="form-label fw-semibold text-dark">Nome da Clínica</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" asp-for="TrialInput.ClinicName" required placeholder="Ex: Clínica Evoluir ABA" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label class="form-label fw-semibold text-dark">CNPJ / CPF da Clínica</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" asp-for="TrialInput.CNPJ" placeholder="Ex: 00.000.000/0000-00" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label class="form-label fw-semibold text-dark">E-mail do Administrador (Login)</label>
                                    <input type="email" class="form-control" asp-for="TrialInput.AdminEmailAddress" required placeholder="Ex: admin@clinicaevoluir.com" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label class="form-label fw-semibold text-dark">Senha de Acesso</label>
                                    <input type="password" class="form-control" asp-for="TrialInput.AdminPassword" required placeholder="Digite uma senha forte" minlength="6" />
                                    <small class="text-muted">Utilize pelo menos 6 caracteres contendo letras e números.</small>
                                </div>
                                <div class="d-flex justify-content-end gap-2 mt-4 pt-3 border-top">
                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary rounded-pill px-4" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Cancelar</button>
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-interactive rounded-pill px-4">
                                        Iniciar Avaliação Grátis <i class="fa fa-arrow-right ms-1"></i>
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        }
    }
    }
}

